snippet.title: Winter Survival Simulator Teaser
snippet.description:
Add it to your wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1394960/Winter_Survival_Simulator/
Teaser featuring in-game footage from Winter Survival Simulator.
Dive into the ultimate winter survival experience and see if you can survive long enough for rescue to arrive.
